        Compassionate oncology nurse and yoga instructor with options for various approaches to yoga practice including, but not limited to Vinyasa flow, Power flow, Yin and Restorative for adults.

        Over 14 years of various types of yoga practices, including meditation and Yoga Nidra.

        Over 14 years of experience working with organizations specializing in inpatient and outpatient health care. Resourceful and well versed in dealing with multilevel needs (emotional and physical) within a multidisciplinary team and independently. Able to work effectively with patients, families, and members of the multidisciplinary team to optimize patient outcomes.

