        My meditation practices are based in my own experiences of meditation as well as teachings from the Vedas, Dr. Deepak Chopra, Ester Ekhart, and Jana Roemer.

        And finally, my asana/movement practices originate in the Yoga Sutras, with formal training (200H YTT) from Altr Yoga (Yoga Alliance Certified), Calgary, AB, Canada, Yoga Thrive, and Jana Roemer.

